{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"So I'm here to tell you a story of success from Africa."},{"time":4000,"text":"A year and a half ago,"},{"time":7000,"text":"four of the five people who are full time members"},{"time":9000,"text":"at Ushahidi,"},{"time":11000,"text":"which means \"testimony\" in Swahili,"},{"time":14000,"text":"were TED Fellows."},{"time":16000,"text":"A year ago in Kenya we had post-election violence."},{"time":19000,"text":"And in that time we prototyped and built,"},{"time":22000,"text":"in about three days, a system that would allow"},{"time":24000,"text":"anybody with a mobile phone"},{"time":26000,"text":"to send in information and reports on what was happening around them."},{"time":29000,"text":"We took what we knew about Africa,"},{"time":31000,"text":"the default device,"},{"time":33000,"text":"the mobile phone, as our common denominator,"},{"time":35000,"text":"and went from there."},{"time":37000,"text":"We got reports like this."},{"time":44000,"text":"This is just a couple of them from January 17th, last year."},{"time":50000,"text":"And our system was rudimentary. It was very basic."},{"time":53000,"text":"It was a mash-up that used data that we collected from people,"},{"time":56000,"text":"and we put it on our map."}]},{"cues":[{"time":58000,"text":"But then we decided we needed to do something more."},{"time":60000,"text":"We needed to take what we had built"},{"time":62000,"text":"and create a platform out of it so that it could be used elsewhere in the world."},{"time":65000,"text":"And so there is a team of developers"},{"time":68000,"text":"from all over Africa, who are part of this team now --"},{"time":71000,"text":"from Ghana, from Malawi, from Kenya."},{"time":73000,"text":"There is even some from the U.S."},{"time":77000,"text":"We're building for smartphones, so that it can be used in the developed world,"},{"time":80000,"text":"as well as the developing world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":82000,"text":"We are realizing that this is true."},{"time":84000,"text":"If it works in Africa then it will work anywhere."},{"time":86000,"text":"And so we build for it in Africa first"},{"time":89000,"text":"and then we move to the edges."},{"time":91000,"text":"It's now been deployed in the Democratic Republic of the Congo."},{"time":94000,"text":"It's being used by NGOs all over East Africa,"},{"time":97000,"text":"small NGOs doing their own little projects."},{"time":100000,"text":"Just this last month it was deployed by"},{"time":102000,"text":"Al Jazeera in Gaza."},{"time":105000,"text":"But that's actually not what I'm here to talk about."}]},{"cues":[{"time":107000,"text":"I'm here to talk about the next big thing,"},{"time":109000,"text":"because what we're finding out is that"},{"time":111000,"text":"we have this capacity to report"},{"time":113000,"text":"eyewitness accounts of what's going on in real time."},{"time":117000,"text":"We're seeing this in events like Mumbai recently,"},{"time":120000,"text":"where it's so much easier to report now"},{"time":122000,"text":"than it is to consume it."},{"time":124000,"text":"There is so much information; what do you do?"},{"time":126000,"text":"This is the Twitter reports for over three days"},{"time":129000,"text":"just covering Mumbai."},{"time":131000,"text":"How do you decide what is important?"},{"time":133000,"text":"What is the veracity level of what you're looking at?"},{"time":136000,"text":"So what we find is that there is this"},{"time":138000,"text":"great deal of wasted crisis information"},{"time":140000,"text":"because there is just too much information for us to"},{"time":143000,"text":"actually do anything with right now."},{"time":146000,"text":"And what we're actually really concerned with"},{"time":148000,"text":"is this first three hours."},{"time":150000,"text":"What we are looking at is the first three hours."},{"time":152000,"text":"How do we deal with that information that is coming in?"},{"time":155000,"text":"You can't understand what is actually happening."},{"time":157000,"text":"On the ground and around the world"},{"time":159000,"text":"people are still curious,"},{"time":161000,"text":"and trying to figure out what is going on. But they don't know."}]},{"cues":[{"time":164000,"text":"So what we built of course, Ushahidi,"},{"time":167000,"text":"is crowdsourcing this information."},{"time":169000,"text":"You see this with Twitter, too. You get this information overload."},{"time":172000,"text":"So you've got a lot of information. That's great."},{"time":174000,"text":"But now what?"},{"time":176000,"text":"So we think that there is something interesting we can do here."},{"time":179000,"text":"And we have a small team who is working on this."},{"time":181000,"text":"We think that we can actually create"},{"time":183000,"text":"a crowdsourced filter."},{"time":185000,"text":"Take the crowd and apply them to the information."},{"time":188000,"text":"And by rating it and by rating"},{"time":190000,"text":"the different people who submit information,"},{"time":192000,"text":"we can get refined results"},{"time":194000,"text":"and weighted results."},{"time":196000,"text":"So that we have a better understanding"},{"time":198000,"text":"of the probability of something being true or not."},{"time":200000,"text":"This is the kind of innovation that is,"},{"time":203000,"text":"quite frankly -- it's interesting that it's coming from Africa."},{"time":205000,"text":"It's coming from places that you wouldn't expect."},{"time":208000,"text":"From young, smart developers."},{"time":210000,"text":"And it's a community around it that has decided to build this."},{"time":213000,"text":"So, thank you very much."},{"time":215000,"text":"And we are very happy to be part of the TED family."},{"time":217000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}